summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and the City Comptroller to draw a warrant on the General Fund in favor of the Clerk of the Superior Court of King County to settle judgments and cost in Cause No. 62279 on account of the changing and establishing of the grade of the alleys in Blocks One (1) and Two (2), Crown Addition to the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 18452.
